Class CiscoNxBgpVrfNeighborAddressFamilyConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.representation.cisco.nx.CiscoNxBgpVrfNeighborAddressFamilyConfiguration

    java.io.Serializable

    public class CiscoNxBgpVrfNeighborAddressFamilyConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents the BGP configuration for a single address family in a single BGP neighbor.

    Configuration commands entered at the CLI config-router-neighbor-af or config-router-vrf-neighbor-af levels.
